data.description: Introducing this charming 4-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom residence nestled on a generous .52-acre lot. Boasting a spacious floor plan, the home offers ample room for comfortable living and entertaining. A standout feature is the expansive 4-car garage, complete with a convenient lean-to and a concrete patio perfect for outdoor gatherings. The remodeled full bathroom exudes modern elegance, while a generously sized laundry room adds a practical touch. Enjoy the convenience of stainless steel appliances in the kitchen. Located in a highly desirable area, this property offers a blend of comfort, style, and functionality for its fortunate new owners. Seller is licensed real estate agent. Recent updates: New Roof singles on house in 2017, furnace and central air 2018, main level flooring 2023, water heater 2020, full bathroom remodel 2020. Call today for a private showing.
